sentences.sentence: I visited the birds, mice, cats, dogs, budgies, hamsters, rabbits and so on.
sentences.translation: 我参观了鸟，鼠，猫，狗，虎皮鹦鹉，仓鼠，兔子等。

sentences.sentence: I visited the birds, mice, cats, dogs, budgies, hamsters, rabbits and so on.
sentences.translation: 我看到了鸟，老鼠，猫，狗，鹦鹉，仓鼠及兔子等等。

sentences.sentence: Two morons stand on a cliff with their arms outstretched. One has some budgies lined up on each arm, the other has parrots lined up on his arms.
sentences.translation: 两个傻瓜站在悬崖边，伸展双臂。其中一个傻瓜在胳膊上捆了一排虎皮鹦鹉，另一个也绑了鹦鹉。
